(15, 1, '2017-10-11 18:15:48', '2017-10-11 18:15:48', '<p style=\"margin: 40px 0 60px; text-align: center;\"><a class=\"action-btn\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DpoWEBipUtI\" data-lity><i class=\"fa fa-play-circle\"></i>Watch Demo</a></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clearfix wow fadeIn animated animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; -webkit-animation-duration: 1.5s; -moz-animation-duration: 1.5s; animation-duration: 1.5s;\" data-wow-duration=\"1.5s\">\r\n<div class=\"col-third col-first\">\r\n<h4><i class=\"ontop fa fa-car\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #81b3ab;\"></i> Easy.</h4>\r\nJust download MyGreenCar and choose the cars you have your eyes on. MyGreenCar detects when you\'re driving and records your trips. It then automatically calculates how different cars stack up for you.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-third\">\r\n<h4><i class=\"ontop fa fa-calculator\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #81b3ab;\"></i> Precise.</h4>\r\nOur vehicle physics models are rigorously validated. MyGreenCar compares your fuel costs in any car, or for EVs predicts your range viability and charging needs. Take the guesswork out of comparing cars.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-third col-last\">\r\n<h4><i class=\"ontop fa fa-bar-chart\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #81b3ab;\"></i> Personalized.</h4>\r\nCompare any car for your unique driving. MyGreenCar accounts for how far you\'re driving, what hills you go up and down, what traffic you get stuck in, whether you\'re a lead-foot or ecodriver, and more.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"viewportSize\" style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 0px; right: 0px; z-index: 99999999; background-color: #000000; color: #ffffff; font-family: Menlo; font-size: 11px; line-height: 20px; width: 85px; text-align: center;\"></div>', 'How it works', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-it-works', '', '', '2018-08-15 19:17:21', '2018-08-15 19:17:21', '', 13, 'http://localhost:8888/mgc_front_page/?page_id=15', 1, 'page', '', 0),
