(144, 1, '2017-10-17 16:08:08', '2017-10-17 16:08:08', '<p>We are a team of highly enthusiastic researchers, engineers and developers, working on MyGreenCar project for several years from the Lawrence Berkeley National Laboratory. We all believe that choosing a vehicle is a critical decision point with huge implications for our environment.</p>\r\n<p>Passionate about energy efficiency, we aim to follow the steps of our predecessor Dr Rosenfeld and help people reduce their consumptions along with their expenses.</p> ', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '111-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-17 16:08:08', '2017-10-17 16:08:08', '', 111, 'http://localhost:8888/mgc_front_page/2017/10/17/111-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
