(174, 1, '2017-10-19 13:01:01', '2017-10-19 13:01:01', '<div class=\"clearfix wow fadeIn animated animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; -webkit-animation-duration: 1.5s; -moz-animation-duration: 1.5s; animation-duration: 1.5s;\" data-wow-duration=\"1.5s\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-third col-first\">\r\n<h4><i class=\"ontop fa fa-car\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #81b3ab;\"></i> Easy.</h4>\r\nSimply download the App and select the cars which caught your interest. Then drive your current car just as you would normally do.\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-third\">\r\n<h4><i class=\"ontop fa fa-calculator\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #81b3ab;\"></i> Precise.</h4>\r\nOur mathematical models, developed over years of experience, simulate the cars you have selected on your everyday shifts.\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-third col-last\">\r\n<h4><i class=\"ontop fa fa-bar-chart\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #81b3ab;\"></i> Personalized.</h4>\r\nCompare how each car performs in fuel economy, battery states-of-charge and more, for your specific driving.\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'How it works', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-19 13:01:01', '2017-10-19 13:01:01', '', 15, 'http://localhost:8888/mgc_front_page/2017/10/19/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(175, 1, '2017-10-20 11:32:34', '2017-10-20 11:32:34', '<p>Ever wonder if an electric car is right for you? Eliminate range anxiety by seeing how different EVs stack up in their range viability. Understand how and where you might need to charge your future EV to meet your trip needs. Verify if you need to buy a special charger for your home, or whether you\'d be just fine with 120V wall outlet in your garage. See if you even need a charger at your work or at other places - all for your unique driving.</p>', 'Thinking about an EV?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ev-batteries', '', '', '2017-11-02 15:15:37', '2017-11-02 15:15:37', '', 13, 'http://localhost:8888/mgc_front_page/?page_id=175', 4, 'page', '', 0),
(177, 1, '2017-10-20 11:32:34', '2017-10-20 11:32:34', '<p>If you are considering buying Electrical vehicles, MyGreenCar calculates the states of charge of their batteries during each trip. You are then able to check which ones would be able to make it through your day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Manually add the charging points around you or let us detect them automatically. You can also set a specific electricity price for each one of them to make your results as precise as possible.</p>', 'Monitor your batteries', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '175-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-20 11:32:34', '2017-10-20 11:32:34', '', 175, 'http://localhost:8888/mgc_front_page/2017/10/20/175-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
