(186, 1, '2017-10-23 16:31:17', '2017-10-23 16:31:17', '<p id=\"about_mgc\">MyGreenCar is your virtual test drive. Compare cars for your unique driving.</p>\r\n<!--</p><a href=\"https://www.lbl.gov/\"><img id=\"berkeley-lab-logo\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/mgc_front_page/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/berkeley_lab_logo-1-1024x233.png\" alt=\"Berkeley Lab\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-131\" /></a>-->', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '60-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-23 16:31:17', '2017-10-23 16:31:17', '', 60, 'http://localhost:8888/mgc_front_page/2017/10/23/60-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(187, 1, '2017-10-23 16:34:14', '2017-10-23 16:34:14', '<div class=\"clearfix wow fadeIn animated animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; -webkit-animation-duration: 1.5s; -moz-animation-duration: 1.5s; animation-duration: 1.5s;\" data-wow-duration=\"1.5s\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-third col-first\">\r\n<h4><i class=\"ontop fa fa-car\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #81b3ab;\"></i> Easy.</h4>\r\nJust download the App and drive around like normal in your current car. MyGreenCar automatically detects when youre driving and records your trip. Pick whichever cars you want to compare from our massive database of vehicle models and see how any car compares for your unique driving.\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-third\">\r\n<h4><i class=\"ontop fa fa-calculator\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #81b3ab;\"></i> Precise.</h4>\r\nOur vehicle physics models are rigorously validated. MyGreenCar compares your fuel costs in any car, or for EVs predicts your range viability and charging needs.\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-third col-last\">\r\n<h4><i class=\"ontop fa fa-bar-chart\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #81b3ab;\"></i> Personalized.</h4>\r\nCompare any car for your unique driving. MyGreenCar accounts for how far youre driving, what hills you go up and down, what traffic you get stuck in, whether youre a lead-foot or ecodriver, and more.\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'How it works', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-23 16:34:14', '2017-10-23 16:34:14', '', 15, 'http://localhost:8888/mgc_front_page/2017/10/23/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(188, 1, '2017-10-23 16:43:48', '2017-10-23 16:43:48', '<p>We want to save you money. Along the way, we help save the planet.</p> \r\n<p>We help car buyers see how much money theyll save with a gr$$ner car. We define green in the broadest possible sense... Interested in an EV but not sure about range or charging? Great, we can help! Thinking about a Hybrid but not sure if itll pay off? Cool, we can help with that too. Need a pickup truck for your lifestyle? No problem, well help you find the pickup that saves you the most money on fuel for your unique needs and driving patterns.</p>\r\n<p>We want millions of people to see how choosing a gr$$ner car is easy and affordable. Along the way, we help prevent gigatons (thats a lot!) of global carbon emissions.</p>\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Our Mission', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '93-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-23 16:43:48', '2017-10-23 16:43:48', '', 93, 'http://localhost:8888/mgc_front_page/2017/10/23/93-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(189, 1, '2017-10-23 16:45:59', '2017-10-23 16:45:59', '<p>Select from our database of vehicle physics models - we have virtually every car on the market! From conventionals, to hybrids, to electrics, to SUVs and pickup trucks your next car is here!</p>\r\n<p>Tell MyGreenCar which car you currently drive and well compare cars against your current car, for your unique driving.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Compare virtually any car!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '83-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-23 16:45:59', '2017-10-23 16:45:59', '', 83, 'http://localhost:8888/mgc_front_page/2017/10/23/83-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
