(192, 1, '2017-10-23 16:50:38', '2017-10-23 16:50:38', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">MyGreenCar was developed by Lawrence Berkeley National Laboratory, where we Bring Science Solutions to the World. Founded in 1931 by Ernest Orlando Lawrence, a physicist who won the Nobel Prize for the invention of the Cyclotron, Berkeley Lab is now associated with Thirteen Nobel prizes. In particular, our inspiration for MyGreenCar comes from the late Arthur Rosenfeld, a distinguished scientist from Berkeley Lab. In what is sometimes called the Rosenfeld effect, Arts work has helped bring about Californias energy efficiency revolution.</p>\r\n<p>Our team strives to create a Rosenfeld effect in the transportation sector. We want to help prevent gigatons of carbon emissions while saving YOU money.</p> ', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '111-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-23 16:50:38', '2017-10-23 16:50:38', '', 111, 'http://localhost:8888/mgc_front_page/2017/10/23/111-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
