(203, 1, '2017-10-24 12:31:27', '2017-10-24 12:31:27', '<p>We want to save you money. Along the way, we help save the planet.</p> \r\n<p>We want you to see how much money you can save in a greener car. We want to take the guess work out of car shopping. We define green in the broadest possible sense. Interested in an EV but not sure about range or charging? Thinking about a Hybrid but not sure if itll pay off? Need a pickup truck for your lifestyle? We help answer all of these questions - all personalized to your unique needs and driving patterns.</p>\r\n<p>We want millions of people to see how choosing a greener car is easy and affordable. Along the way, we help prevent gigatons of global carbon emissions (thats a lot!).</p>\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Our Mission', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '93-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-24 12:31:27', '2017-10-24 12:31:27', '', 93, 'http://localhost:8888/mgc_front_page/2017/10/24/93-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(205, 1, '2017-10-24 12:46:21', '2017-10-24 12:46:21', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">MyGreenCar was developed by Lawrence Berkeley National Laboratory, home to thirteen Nobel prizes. The Labs motto, Bring Science Solutions to the World is a mantra for the MyGreenCar team. We are inspired by the late Arthur Rosenfeld, a distinguished scientist from Berkeley Lab, who helped bring about Californias energy efficiency revolution.</p>\r\n<p>Our team strives to create a <a href=\"http://newscenter.lbl.gov/2017/01/27/art-rosenfeld-californias-godfather-energy-efficiency-90/\" target=\"_blank\">Rosenfeld effect</a> in the transportation sector. We want to help prevent gigatons of carbon emissions while saving YOU money.</p> ', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '111-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-24 12:46:21', '2017-10-24 12:46:21', '', 111, 'http://localhost:8888/mgc_front_page/2017/10/24/111-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
