(216, 1, '2017-10-25 08:37:03', '2017-10-25 08:37:03', '<p>We want to save you money. Along the way, we help save the planet.</p> \r\n<p>We want you to see how much money you can save in a greener car. Our goal is to take the guesswork out of car shopping. We define green in the broadest possible sense. Need a pickup truck and wondering if one of the new aluminum body pickups makes sense? Thinking about a Hybrid but not sure if itll pay off? Interested in an EV but not sure about range or charging? We help answer all of these questions  all personalized to your unique needs and driving patterns.</p>\r\n<p>We want millions of people to see how choosing a greener car is easy and affordable. Along the way, we help prevent gigatons of global carbon emissions (thats a lot!)</p>\r\n \r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n', 'Our Mission', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '93-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-25 08:37:03', '2017-10-25 08:37:03', '', 93, 'http://localhost:8888/mgc_front_page/2017/10/25/93-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
